title: Ma Baker
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Western, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small bakery and coffee shop in Karrtorp offers a menu that is largely vegetarian with vegan choices. Uses all organic ingredients in soups, vegetable dishes, made-in-house bread, buns, cakes and hearty sandwiches. Wi-Fi. Has games for you to borrow.
